In goes a dusty, tarnished mess and out comes a shiny restored automobile, just in time to hand the keys back to the shocked owner. In the second episode, Tim and Fuzz head to Cheshire to answer an SOS call about a 1938 MG TA, whose owner is unable to restore it to a roadworthy state due to illness.
